    "Ground Zero": {
        type: ["Interpersonal"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The Chinese logistics officer was efficient. Meticulous, even. Every requisition filed correctly, every inventory count verified twice. The squad appreciated the precision. One couldn't get past the accent.</em></p>
            <p>"You know what her people did, right?"</p>
            <p>"She's a logistics officer."</p>
