        description: """
            <h3>Effects</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>The Beilan Island Incident killed 870 million people because one municipal government failed to file a report. The largest single catastrophe in human history, caused by negligence so profound it rewrote the map of the world. You cannot look at someone from that country without seeing the crater where Shanghai used to be.</li>
                <li>You gain 3 strife whenever you must take orders from, rely on, or cooperate closely with a Chinese national.</li>
                <li>The first time this anxiety applies in a scene, you gain 1 fortune point.</li>
