    Pyrophobia: {
        type: ["Mental"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The squad was warming up around a burn barrel. Scrap wood, old packaging, standard field heat. Everyone crowded close. One stood three meters back, arms crossed against the cold.</em></p>
