    Alcoholic: {
        type: ["Mental"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The squad had a tradition: after a successful op, someone would produce a bottle. Cheap stuff, usually. Green Zone rotgut or whatever the local equivalent was. One drink each, toast the living, pour one for the dead. Simple.</em></p>
