    "Chem Addict": {
        type: ["Mental"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The medic noticed first. The operator's pupils were wrong for the lighting, her reaction times a half-beat too fast, her hands too steady for someone who'd been awake for thirty-six hours. She pulled the Commander aside.</em></p>
            <p>"Chen's on something."</p>
            <p>"She passed the pre-op screen."</p>
            <p>"The pre-op screen checks for five compounds. There are forty on the market. She's cycling stims, probably military-grade. Look at her hands."</p>
