        """
    },
    "Shell Shock": {
        type: ["Mental"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The training exercise used blanks and flash charges. Standard stress inoculation. The squad moved through the killhouse by the book. When the first charge went off, eleven operators pushed forward. One dropped flat and covered her head.</em></p>
            <p>"Vasquez, move!"</p>
