    "Dark Secret": {
        type: ["Social"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The background check came back clean. Service record, medical history, financial disclosures: everything verified. The new operator settled in. Three weeks later, the squad's intelligence analyst was organizing old files and stopped on a name.</em></p>
