    Haughty: {
        type: ["Social"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The joint operation required merging with a local militia for the sweep. Their equipment was outdated, their tactics were improvised, and their commander was a former truck driver who'd earned his rank by not dying. The liaison from the professional outfit reviewed the militia's plan and handed it back.</em></p>
