    "Trigger Lock": {
        type: ["Mental"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The hostile had a weapon. Was raising it. The shot was clean, the angle was clear, and the operator had a perfect sight picture. Her finger was on the trigger. She didn't fire.</em></p>
