    "Blunt Instrument": {
        type: ["Mental"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The Commander needed someone to negotiate the supply contract. She asked Griggs. Griggs stared at her like she'd been asked to defuse a bomb with a fork.</em></p>
            <p>"Send someone else."</p>
            <p>"You're the one who knows the supplier."</p>
