                <li>You gain 3 strife whenever you are prevented from taking a dangerous course of action, forced into a safe position, or told to value your own survival over the mission.</li>
                <li>The first time this anxiety applies in a scene, you gain 1 fortune point.</li>
            </ul>
        """
    },
    Superstitious: {
        type: ["Mental"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The op was scheduled for 0600. At 0545, the squad was kitted and ready. One operator was still at her bunk, arranging objects on the footlocker in a specific order: photo, coin, spent casing, patch.</em></p>
            <p>"We're moving in five."</p>
            <p>"I know. One minute."</p>
            <p><em>She touched each object in sequence. Photo, coin, casing, patch. Then again. Photo, coin, casing, patch. Then she turned each one fifteen degrees clockwise. Then she stood up.</em></p>
            <p>"What happens if you don't do that?"</p>
            <p>"I've never not done it."</p>
