                <li>You gain 3 strife whenever you are unable to perform your rituals or routines, whenever your lucky item is lost or unavailable, or whenever someone disrupts or mocks your superstitions.</li>
                <li>The first time this anxiety applies in a scene, you gain 1 fortune point.</li>
            </ul>
        """
    },
    Germaphobe: {
        type: ["Mental"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The squad ate field rations out of the packaging. Standard practice: tear, eat, discard. One operator transferred hers to a personal container first, using utensils she'd sterilized that morning.</em></p>
            <p>"You know those are sealed at the factory, right?"</p>
            <p>"I know where factories are. I've seen the conditions."</p>
            <p>"It's a ration pack."</p>
            <p>"It's a ration pack that was stored in a crate, loaded by someone whose hand hygiene I can't verify, shipped in a vehicle I haven't inspected, and stacked in a depot alongside medical waste containers."</p>
            <p>"There's no medical waste in the supply depot."</p>
            <p>"There was in Sector 4. I checked."</p>
