        """
    },
    Grudge: {
        type: ["Interpersonal"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The transfer request landed on the Commander's desk. Routine reassignment: an operator from another unit joining for the Sector 11 contract. She read the name and set the paperwork down.</em></p>
