    Misanthrope: {
        type: ["Interpersonal"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>The debrief was standard. Commander laid out the objectives, reviewed the timeline, asked for feedback. Most of the squad responded. One sat in the back, arms crossed, saying nothing.</em></p>
            <p>"Seven, you were on overwatch. Anything to add?"</p>
