    Tsundere: {
        type: ["Interpersonal", "Social"],
        flavor: """
            <p><em>Cheeta found her workspace completely reorganized. Tools sorted by size, spare parts labeled, the coffee mug she'd been using as a pencil holder emptied, cleaned, and returned with the pencils sharpened. She looked at Makiatto, who was reading a manual at the next bench over and very deliberately not making eye contact.</em></p>
